msg: httplite: first pass at a suite of test cases for httplite.  Some tests currently fail.

author: marvin
msg: Add disabled test for utf8proc normalization.
Normalization in utf8proc works correctly, in that normalizing a string which
is already normalized is a no-op.  However, utf8proc errors out when fed
either control characters or non-character code points, so we skip the test
